Find your inner ninja with the  all-new LEGO  NINJAGO  Movie  Video
Game! Play as your favorite ninjas, Lloyd, Jay,  Kai,  Cole,  Zane,
Nya and Master Wu to defend their home island of Ninjago  from  the
evil  Lord  Garmadon  and  his  Shark  Army.  Master  the   art  of
Ninjagility by wall-running, high-jumping and battling the  foes of
Ninjago to rank up and upgrade the ninja's combat skills.

For more info go to : https://store.steampowered.com/app/640590/
